    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/86892facd56f4f9b15eb13747cde701e.poster.avif?t=1751798588\" width=548 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/86892facd56f4f9b15eb13747cde701e.webm?t=1751798588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GhostPub是一款类Roguelike的模拟经营游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/0a7dabbdf5083404d40f03997a7f9f00.webp?t=1751798588\" width=560 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/2cba29b30873e0e935c7348d451b7c14.avif?t=1751798588\" width=554 height=308 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/d65884460c7acdc25912a18087af49c9.avif?t=1751798588\" width=560 height=207 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让我们一起寻找并调制各种鸡尾酒吧！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请为前来幽灵酒馆的幽灵们调制合适的鸡尾酒。幽灵们会点各种奇怪的鸡尾酒。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/90b16401020475a389680e08a607033d.avif?t=1751798588\" width=118 height=101 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/48da48b415f6c8ddbeeee9534b92ae06.poster.avif?t=1751798588\" width=261 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/48da48b415f6c8ddbeeee9534b92ae06.webm?t=1751798588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/0a7dabbdf5083404d40f03997a7f9f00.webp?t=1751798588\" width=560 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/0211611ddee759ee01f769d03f41fcf6.poster.avif?t=1751798588\" width=548 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/0211611ddee759ee01f769d03f41fcf6.webm?t=1751798588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/84722ad68cd32a7bc3cee08cb46eb8c3.avif?t=1751798588\" width=554 height=308 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营酒馆可不轻松。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们应该好好打扫一下幽灵们逗留过的地方。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对幽灵客人偶尔的“意外状况”，要更加勤快地清理。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/46dad4ead0ced6f1c0eb3ddbd78f4198.poster.avif?t=1751798588\" width=88 height=79 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/46dad4ead0ced6f1c0eb3ddbd78f4198.webm?t=1751798588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/053e9de7932e25ca50d595a26b7aedaf.avif?t=1751798588\" width=88 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/0a7dabbdf5083404d40f03997a7f9f00.webp?t=1751798588\" width=560 height=48 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>赚钱不容易吧？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/98daee919afca20aa941aaee1e34e50a.avif?t=1751798588\" width=554 height=308 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>但别担心。</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花钱开启宝箱，获取随机卡牌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣新的员工，扩展你的酒馆。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各种卡牌，扩大你的酒馆。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/0a7dabbdf5083404d40f03997a7f9f00.webp?t=1751798588\" width=560 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/e751f3cb42629ff557e43de1dbef3b5f.avif?t=1751798588\" width=554 height=308 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你能承受住压力吗？</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着回合推进，看着酒馆成长，并发现新的鸡尾酒配方吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调酒时，别忘了随时查阅你的配方书，以免出错。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你的心脏槽清空，就要重新开始回合了。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/9c96bd4c823489a1ef7330765b455070.avif?t=1751798588\" width=554 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>哎呀！酒馆倒闭了。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>再试一次吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/b16c268a9e638b23e129ae831e5cc966.poster.avif?t=1751798588\" width=128 height=147 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/b16c268a9e638b23e129ae831e5cc966.webm?t=1751798588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/0a7dabbdf5083404d40f03997a7f9f00.webp?t=1751798588\" width=560 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/f86edec0bec6267f05f00774f7153463.poster.avif?t=1751798588\" width=548 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337710/extras/f86edec0bec6267f05f00774f7153463.webm?t=1751798588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>应对越来越多的桌子和幽灵客人！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不要停下。继续工作。继续努力！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>即使酒馆垮了，幽灵酒馆也必须继续运营。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>看看你能坚持到哪一步。</strong></h2>",
